<author>Thanher</author>
<title>Tatsate Chawlhdamna</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A thanuoi dailim nuoi achun,
 Tatsate kichawl dam tan au;
 A maua kumsawt guo bang hinna,
 A chantieng uh-kipak tan au.

[V2]
 Cheng untin kichawldam tan au,
 Lungsietna Lalpa chawian in;
 Kumsawt ninnuom laituol leng tan au,
 A thanuoi dailim nuoma chun.

[V3]
 2. A thanuoi dailim nuom achun,
 Alang dah sawl-ang bang tan au;
 Hinna damtui a nga bang buolin,
 Vuk sangin le vam zaw tan au.

[V4]
 3. A thanuoi dailim nuom achun,
 Kah leh lungdawnna umta lo;
 Gitloh huihpi leh thepna gal lien,
 A bei tai khawpi nuom achun.

[V5]
 4. Gam ninnuom a laituol lengte,
 Nuoi simlei lungngaihna pel in:
 Van kingkang gihawih tawh van tuolnuom,
 A lengui Lal Krista lawiin.</lyrics>
</song>